{"tid":820764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Made in Japan梗好野]無印良品MUJI日式豆沙夾心燒餅包裝疑發霉　全線下架","createTime":"2018-09-15T15:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T12:02:16.000Z","uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84043d5cac18856c61154536e5596520336b6f27","tid":820764,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/231855_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F231855_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=6e0a4ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無印良品（MUJI）一款日式豆沙夾心燒餅的包裝可能有發霉，食環署食安中心呼籲市民不要食用。無印較早前已把所有受影響產品下架和停售，及主動回收。<br />\n<br />\nMUJI日式豆沙夾心燒餅的包裝可能有發霉的情況，MUJI已將所有受影響產品下架和停售，及主動回收。（MUJI網頁）<br />\nMUJI日式豆沙夾心燒餅的包裝可能有發霉的情況，MUJI已將所有受影響產品下架和停售，及主動回收。（MUJI網頁）<br />\n<br />\n食安中心透過恆常食物事故監察系統，得悉新加坡農業食品與獸醫局發出通告，指無印良品（新加坡）在當地回收一批次的日式豆沙夾心燒餅，因為有關產品的包裝可能出現發霉情況。中心得悉事件後，隨即與無印良品（香港）有限公司跟進。<br />\n<br />\n食安中心指，根據該公司提供的資料，曾進口有關產品，並在旗下分店發售。該公司較早前已把所有受影響產品下架和停售及主動回收。市民可於辦公時間致電其熱線2694 9309查詢上述產品的回收事宜。中心會繼續跟進和採取適當行動。<br />\n<br />\n有關產品資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n產品名稱：日式豆沙夾心燒餅<br />\n<br />\n品牌：無印良品<br />\n<br />\n來源地：日本<br />\n<br />\n包裝：每包135克<br />\n<br />\n有效食用日期：2018年9月12日至12月5日"},{"pid":"79e9f137a073915d5d98fe03dce4616abdf689fb","tid":820764,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:33:31.000Z","msg":"親日犬はどこですか。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05a9ae25c5eb663396855d329396cd423d5e140","tid":820764,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e291388b7989827e83a188672ffd2fc8ca53d83","tid":820764,"uid":208799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:53:21.000Z","msg":"made in china 嘢"},{"pid":"8b788798f722a3f37e50733dc71fa6750578a9a5","tid":820764,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e291388b7989827e83a188672ffd2fc8ca53d83","tid":820764,"uid":208799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:53:21.000Z","msg":"made in china 嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"來源地日本"},{"pid":"5ec9986820d27d661cdb8b903b4e750383787a9e","tid":820764,"uid":209487,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8b671e3dbb772289117f17c647bc2dd079cee5d","tid":820764,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5ec9986820d27d661cdb8b903b4e750383787a9e","tid":820764,"uid":209487,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"親日犬を揶揄して楽しいだ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4757923aaedf6a1f26c0404a517938103803910d","tid":820764,"uid":9298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"咁d 芝士同腐乳又唔駛落架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b7c8fbdbfec966258b9e90763c0f38860d5cdd","tid":820764,"uid":209487,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e0f37edbf3f3d60e4fac5910da2c90e9e42add9","tid":820764,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6b7c8fbdbfec966258b9e90763c0f38860d5cdd","tid":820764,"uid":209487,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8b671e3dbb772289117f17c647bc2dd079cee